    "content": "Sure, I can guide you through placing the order using your gift card. Here are the steps you can follow:\n\n1. Go to our online store.\n2. Find the Blue M t-shirt in the product catalog.\n3. Add it to your cart.\n4. Proceed to checkout.\n5. During the payment step, select 'Gift Card' as the payment method.\n6. Enter your gift card ID and PIN if required.\n7. Complete the purchase.\n\nIf you need further assistance during these steps, feel free to ask."
